{"tid":336054,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"加入「新神獸」 Pokémon GO熱潮再起","createTime":"2017-07-26T06:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T06:52:40.000Z","uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad61c654db76a66528f5c1b8f6ed0ea637460b2","tid":336054,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:02:14.000Z","msg":"手機遊戲Pok&eacute;mon GO去年暑假推出時，一度掀起全港「捉精靈」熱潮。隨着遊戲近日推出「新神獸」，機迷紛紛拿起手機，全港多區再湧現「捉精靈」人潮。為捕捉最新神獸「急凍鳥」和「利基亞」，前日（24日）藍田匯景花園附近已有近千位「訓練員」聚集，昨（25日）大埔、荃灣、鰂魚涌等地亦有數十人「出動」，在街上巡遊尋找小精靈。因今次神獸屬限時推出，不少網友都在fb群組通風報信，務求能趕及將神獸據為己有<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/LnCS0VI_I4RdpeT.Fs9Z3A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/skypost/26JAE002__20170726_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FLnCS0VI_I4RdpeT.Fs9Z3A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fskypost%2F26JAE002__20170726_L.jpg&h=6fa7eadc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e89c4b8eb03ceadf5b84ece578a9a10b7e092ab","tid":336054,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:08:22.000Z","msg":"呢度唔係港大咩"},{"pid":"11f5888cfacfb77cd70c25e970a51dbdacb22e19","tid":336054,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b846ced99be481ed008285eace6d364c598ccd4f","tid":336054,"uid":81185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:12:28.000Z","msg":"如果早十個月出既話可能成萬人捉都似"},{"pid":"3c8e1851d1ba1c6d691f5839ec73c163b7460fd8","tid":336054,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:18:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度唔係港大咩</blockquote><br />\n新聞寫d人捉到去hku"},{"pid":"35b874efd4e84e3fd1a6596fde00497f262eaa8f","tid":336054,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:26